    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接下爷爷的老铺子，修好客人宝贝的东西，有可能是铃铛，有可能是望远镜，也可能是玩具或者茶壶，林子里的大家每一个都有不同的东西需要你帮忙修补！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/2f895a356a5c07f4a0e3ddc60a43910c.poster.avif?t=1771862944\" width=1170 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/2f895a356a5c07f4a0e3ddc60a43910c.webm?t=1771862944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/2f895a356a5c07f4a0e3ddc60a43910c.mp4?t=1771862944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮客人修补古董、传家宝和他们心爱的杯子，每件东西都有一个不一样的谜题！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在菜园种些浆果，调出各种色彩的颜料，然后画出你的五彩缤纷</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >给作品加上一抹你的颜色，然后卖出一个好价钱</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >及时打扫卫生，不要让炉火熄灭，记得给饼干罐子添饼干，保证店里始终井井有条</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑选自己喜欢的家具、地垫之类的东西，把铺子变成自己喜爱的模样！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/fef44dd412d95701d7f2e655201d487f.poster.avif?t=1771862944\" width=1170 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/fef44dd412d95701d7f2e655201d487f.webm?t=1771862944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179050/extras/fef44dd412d95701d7f2e655201d487f.mp4?t=1771862944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运用各种颜色和材料赋予店里你自己的特色，种东西，调颜料，帮客人收拾好他们送来的东西，给邻居烤些饼干，听一听大家的八卦。准备好撸起袖子，接手爷爷的铺子了吗？</p>",
